subject: Re: Monday, continued-3
author: Frank Sumption
full_text:
I knew that! When I heard Janet my brain kinda locked on to that name. 

 I'm still not sure what to think of these supposed technicians on the 
other side. I never get anything that says they are technicians. I get 
some technical sounding information, but it's usually useless. 

 There is some tricky stuff that comes through, so you have to not take 
it all as gosple.  

 Frank
